{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fill the universe with even more life in Reus 2: Ice Age!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Re-create the prehistoric Ice Age with this brand new expansion, filled with biotica that have unique synergies with your worlds ecosystem.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New Biome - Ice Age Tundra</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Variation of Aegir, the mighty Frost Giant</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40+ new biotica, including apexes and cohorts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New archetypes like Evolve and Extinct, building around early biotica to empower future ones</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333960/extras/Reus2_iceage_biotica_GIF.gif?t=1740089830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>New Leaders</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With 4 new leaders to explore, see how their personalities and desires shift the direction of humanity:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Painter</strong> - Wants to unlock as much as possible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The General</strong> - Gains bonuses to military</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Poet</strong> - Improves projects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Villain</strong> - Thrives in a hateful world</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333960/extras/Reus2_iceage_leaders_GIF.gif?t=1740089830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>New Eras</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are also 4 new eras across the development of humanity to experience, giving even more opportunities to create thriving worlds or lead humanity to a spectacular end!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hunter Age</strong> - Crops don't grow easily in this weather so humans must hunt to survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enlightenment</strong> - Minds brimming with ideas, embrace an age of invention!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Nuclear War -</strong> Create nuclear weapons and potentially blow up the entire planet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Age of Discovery</strong> - A planet full of biomes and adventures, humans love to collect oddities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333960/extras/Reus2_iceage_eras_GIF.gif?t=1740089830\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3333960?t=1740089830","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3333960?t=1740089830","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333960/6154e0f30e6f8cac00f16d254dea6d16c0b6b2a7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740089830","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333960/6154e0f30e6f8cac00f16d254dea6d16c0b6b2a7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740089830","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fill the universe with even more life in Reus 2: Ice Age!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Re-create the prehistoric Ice Age with this brand new expansion, filled with biotica that have unique synergies with your worlds ecosystem.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New Biome -